item.title: FM4 Interview mit Markus Lust re. WWE Scandal
item.description: Vince McMahon, the 78 year old founder of World Wrestling Entertainment has resigned from wrestling giant TKO Group and the company it owns and he founded –WWE. . A lawsuit has accused him of serious sexual crimes. A former employee has sued McMahon alleging sexual assault, trafficking and emotional abuse. Riem Higazi spoke with author, creative director and wrestling expert Markus Lust about the WWE scandal and the future of wrestling…. Sendungshinweis: FM4. OKFM4, 29.01.2024, 17 Uhr Feed: https://podcast.orf.at/podcast/fm4/fm4_interviewpodcast/fm4_interviewpodcast.xml
